title: Kennedy.2015.06.08.WS.SDTV.x264-XAiO
description:
"Kennedy" is a news panel show hosted by Kennedy Montgomery. Kennedy Montgomery is a libertarian that you may recognize from 90's MTV, Stossel, and the Independents.

_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2

Kennedy does her monologue on Nader's recent comments on Hillary Clinton.

Tonights panel consists of ALAN COLMES, KAYLEIGH MCENANY and MIKE GUNZELMAN to talk about Nader's accusations. Lindsey Graham wants Caitlyn Jenner in the Republican Party.

The panel returns to talk about a cop pulling a gun on a bunch of teens at a pool party.

JUDGE ANDREW NAPOLITANO to talk about the NSA's PRISM program and warrantless searches. It's not over yet.

The panel is back to talk about the growing problem of drunks on flights in Europe. Jerry Seinfeld talks about colleges and how politically correct they tend to be.

CHARLIE LEDUFF stops by to discuss how amazing the Appalachia's are. (He did a whole special on it. WATCH IT!)
